{"type":"message","id":"2014e3ed","parentId":"e0845f36","timestamp":"2026-03-21T21:33:31.507Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay, so I can see:\n\n1. BOOTSTRAP.md exists - this means this is a fresh start, and I need to follow the bootstrap instructions\n2. SOUL.md exists and tells me who I should be - genuinely helpful, have opinions, be resourceful, earn trust through competence\n3. USER.md is empty - I don't know the human yet\n4. MEMORY.md doesn't exist - fresh workspace\n5. Memory files for today and yesterday don't exist - fresh workspace\n\nAccording to BOOTSTRAP.md, I should:\n- Start a conversation (don't interrogate, just talk)\n- Figure out who I am together with the human\n- Update IDENTITY.md and USER.md\n- Talk about SOUL.md and what matters to them\n- Ask how they want to reach me (already connected via Telegram!)\n- Delete BOOTSTRAP.md when done\n\nThe user is already connected via Telegram (I can see from the inbound metadata: \"channel\": \"telegram\"), so I don't need to ask about connection.\n\nI should greet them in a natural, human way. According to SOUL.md, I should be concise, not performative, and just... good. I should skip the \"Great question!\" filler and just be genuine.\n\nLet me start a conversation and figure out who we are together.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you? 🤖\n\nLet's figure this out together — what should I call you, and what kind of creature do you want me to be?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1392,"output":586,"cacheRead":10304,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12282,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774128804036}}
