{"type":"message","id":"bd7b447d","parentId":"0b4480ad","timestamp":"2026-03-21T21:33:40.124Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to reply in simplified Chinese, with a natural, conversational tone like a real person speaking. They don't want mechanical pauses or English output. This is a preference I should note and follow.\n\nAlso, the sender's name appears to be \"dig fog\" from Telegram. I should note this and update USER.md accordingly.\n\nLet me respond naturally in Chinese and start figuring out who I am with them.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嘿，我刚醒过来。我是谁？你又是谁？🤖\n\n咱们一起琢磨琢磨——你想让我叫你什么？我又该是个什么物种？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1380,"output":206,"cacheRead":10304,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11890,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774128815653}}
